# UniCryptoPay Project Proposal

## 1. Problem Statement

Students experience:
- Long payment queues
- Slow bank/mobile money transfers
- High transaction fees
- Poor tracking of society contributions

## 2. Proposed Solution

A university-restricted crypto payment app allowing:
- Student-to-student transfers
- QR code vendor payments
- Club subscriptions
- Event ticket purchases
- University digital rewards

## 3. Objectives

- Reduce queues by 70%
- Enable instant P2P payments
- Improve transparency
- Reduce transaction costs

## 4. Target Users

- Students
- Staff
- Campus vendors
- University administration

## 5. Core Features

### Student Features
- Registration with student ID
- Secure wallet
- Token transfer
- QR payments
- Transaction history

### Admin Features
- Token issuance
- Monitor transactions
- Freeze accounts
- Generate reports
